title: “Roe Is Dead. Now What?” (Strict Scrutiny Emergency Episode)
description:
Kate, Leah and Melissa discuss the Supreme Court’s egregious decision to end the constitutional right to abortion, and whether other rights could be in jeopardy.
If you want to take action, go to votesaveamerica.com/roe to check out the Fuck Bans Action Plan hub and donate to our Fight Back Fund.
New episodes of Strict Scrutiny drop every Monday. Listen wherever you get your podcasts.
